HEADWORD: Nonprofessional
<hw>Non`pro*fes"sion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not belonging to a profession.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not done by, or proceeding from, professional men;
contrary to professional usage; unprofessional.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonproficiency</ent>⟦br⟧
